  "root_text": {
    "iti55:0.1": "Itivuttaka 55 ",
    "iti55:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti55:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti55:0.4": "Dutiyaesanāsutta ",
    "iti55:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti55:2.1": "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, esanā. ",
    "iti55:2.2": "Katamā tisso? ",
    "iti55:2.3": "Kāmesanā, bhavesanā, brahmacariyesanā—",
    "iti55:2.4": "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso esanā”ti. ",
    "iti55:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti55:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti55:3.1": "“Kāmesanā bhavesanā, ",
    "iti55:3.2": "brahmacariyesanā saha; ",
    "iti55:3.3": "Iti saccaparāmāso, ",
    "iti55:3.4": "diṭṭhiṭṭhānā samussayā. ",
    "iti55:4.1": "Sabbarāgavirattassa, ",
    "iti55:4.2": "taṇhakkhayavimuttino; ",
    "iti55:4.3": "Esanā paṭinissaṭṭhā, ",
    "iti55:4.4": "diṭṭhiṭṭhānā samūhatā; ",
    "iti55:4.5": "Esanānaṁ khayā bhikkhu, ",
    "iti55:4.6": "nirāso akathaṅkathī”ti. ",
    "iti55:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti55:5.2": "Chaṭṭhaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti55:0.1": "So It Was Said 55 ",
    "iti55:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti55:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti55:0.4": "Searches (2nd) ",
    "iti55:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti55:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three searches. ",
    "iti55:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti55:2.3": "The search for sensual pleasures, the search for continued existence, and the search for a spiritual path. ",
    "iti55:2.4": "These are the three searches.” ",
    "iti55:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti55:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti55:3.1": "“The search for sensual pleasures, for a good rebirth, ",
    "iti55:3.2": "and the search for a spiritual path; ",
    "iti55:3.3": "the holding tight to the thought, ‘this is the truth’, ",
    "iti55:3.4": "and the mass of grounds for views—",
    "iti55:4.1": "for one detached from all lusts, ",
    "iti55:4.2": "freed by the ending of craving, ",
    "iti55:4.3": "that searching has been relinquished, ",
    "iti55:4.4": "and those grounds for views eradicated. ",
    "iti55:4.5": "With the ending of searches, a mendicant ",
    "iti55:4.6": "is free of hope and indecision.” ",
    "iti55:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
